[[div class="cyberpunk"]]

[[=]]
+++ __{{05.23.2077}}__
[[/=]]

__Current Objective:__ Avoid ##white|the Man in the White Suit##, comb through the Nobody Archives to figure out his deal (and Nobody's while I'm at it). Assemble the Name Machine.

__Entities of Note:__ Myself (past Nobodies), White Suit

__Concerning Patterns:__
# He knows me almost as well as I know myself. He is the only person to consistently track my location and my contacts. //__How? Why?__//
# Being nonexistent means I can get anywhere. It also means nobody has any clue who the fuck I am, or how to help me. Double-edged sword.


__Activity Since Previous Entry:__

* Broke into Anderson High-Rise for missing part, got New Portland Airwing, Foundation FRFTS, //and// White Suit on my ass
* Lost White Suit in the Xyflex Parade, made my escape in a jacked hovercar
* Met with Foundation contact for Site-30 security guard rotation schedule over waffles
* Infiltrated Site-30 under usual disguise (they never expect the janitors)
* Accessed SCP Foundation database for full information (seems they forgot to revoke my clearance when I stopped existing... keep in mind)
* Downloaded all data on GoI-195 "Nobody"

__Current Status:__ Download complete. Now to do some reading.
@@ @@
